Nokia 105 Dual SIM (Black)
description: Nokia 105 Dual SIM The Nokia 105 is a compact Dual SIM phone that is packed with productivity features. The compact feature phone has a great design and is incredibly lightweight for portability and ease of use. The phone supports Dual SIM functionality which enables it to run two GSM sim cards at the same time. The phone also has a dual standby mode. The Dual SIM functionality enables you to run two Network Services SIM cards at the same time and eliminates the need of carrying two phones with you. The phones supports GSM networks of frequency of 900/1800 MHz. The phone has a compact display of 1.4-inches that has a resolution of 128 x 128 pixels and has support for up to 64K colours. The display can be used to view contact, time and date, and run the productivity applications that come pre loaded with the phone. Lightweight Design and Portability The Nokia 105 has a very compact design. The phone is small in size with a 1.4-inch display and Dual Sim functionality. This enables the phone to be extremely portable. You can easily fit the phone in your pockets, backpack and even in the storage compartment of your vehicle so that it is always easily accessible to you. The phone is powered by Nokia’s Series 30+ Operating system that adds a ton of productivity features to your phone. There is also one year of manufacturers warrant on the device that can be availed easily from any service centre of the company located across major cities. You get a compact phone with a small display and physical keypad. The phone weights only 68grams. The feature phone has easy to use keys and a bright and vivid display that is visible clearly even in sunlight. The UI of the phone is also responsive and provides an immersive experience. Other Features The Nokia 105 comes with a variety of productivity applications and features. You can browse the internet on 2G speeds using the phone’s built in browser. There is also support for up to 2000 contacts in the phone’s contact book. You get an in built FM receiver so that you can enjoy your favourite music. The battery of the phone is a large 800mAH battery that can provide you a standby time of up to 600 hours and a talk time of up to 15 hours on 2G network. The phone also has productivity application such as calculator, converter, clock, calendar, alarm clock, phonebook, etc. There is also an LED light on the phone that can be used as a flashlight torch.
